---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main class="grid grid-flow-row w-[100dvw] overflow-hidden mt-[-4rem]">
    <!-- center line -->
    <!-- <div class="absolute h-full w-[50dvw] border-r"></div> -->

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <div
      class="grid grid-rows-12 h-[100dvh] bg-[url('/img/hero.jpg')] bg-no-repeat bg-cover bg-[center] text-white"
    >
      <div class="row-start-9 row-end-12 text-center font-sans">
        <header class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <p class="text-4xl font-semibold">Solve your Problems</p>
          <p class="text-4xl font-semibold">at the root</p>
          <div class="">
            <a href="/services/" class="p-2 rounded-lg text-xl">Find out how</a>
          </div>
        </header>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Elevator Pitch -->
    <div class="flex flex-col p-5 gap-5 bg-violet-400">
      <div class="">NO MORE STRUGGLING WITH THE SAME PATTERNS FOR YEARS</div>
      <div class="">I AM HERE TO HELP YOU ADDRESS ISSUES ON A ROOT LEVEL</div>
      <div class="">
        you're an amazing self- refleced individual who's read the self help
        books, maybe even done the therapy and always knows how to give the best
        advice. but somehow you never managed to translate that into the big
        changes you want for your own life. i'll let you in on a little
        secret...true change happens when we target the subconscious mind! and
        that's exactly what i know to do best.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Relation -->
    <div class="grid grid-flow-row grid-rows-2 bg-red-500">
      <div class="bg-[url('/img/relate.jpg')] bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-cover">
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col p-5 py-8 gap-5">
        <div class="">I know what it's like</div>
        <div class="">
          <p class="">
            I know what it's like to feel stuck in a loop,with full self
            awareness of certain behaviours, yet no actual practical ways to
            change.
          </p>
          <p class="">
            I know what it's like to have this big AHA moment one day, just to
            find your self in that same old pattern the next. (Read more)
          </p>
          <!-- <button class="border rounded w-max p-2">Book Now</button> -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col p-5 py-8 gap-5 bg-yellow-400 w-[100dvw] overflow-auto"
    >
      <div class="">Testimonials</div>
      <div class="flex overflow-auto gap-2 w-[800px]">
        <div class="w-1/3">
          <div class="">FORGOT MY TROUBLES</div>
          <div class="">
            In a short amount of time I went from really struggling with feeling
            depressed to forgetting that I was ever depressed. Christina's
            methods are really hands on and that's what I love about her
            approach. I really felt in control of my own process and the results
            show it.
          </div>
          <div>- Emily. Y, Entrepreneur</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/3">
          <div class="">LOVELY BISTRO</div>
          <div class="">
            Christina doesn't settle unless she's gotten to the core. She
          </div>
          <div>- Emily. Y, Entrepreneur</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/3">
          <div class="">TRANSPORTED TO PARIS</div>
          <div class="">
            Eating here made me miss Paris so much. What a treat! I will be
            bringing my client meetings here.
          </div>
          <div>- Carly, Entrepreneur</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Offerings -->
    <div class="flex flex-col p-5 gap-5 bg-sky-500">
      <div class="">
        <div class="">
          IT'S TIME TO SOLVE YOUR PROBLEMS AT THE ROOT WITHOUT BEING STUCK FOR
          YEARS!
        </div>
        <div class="">
          I help people reprogram and heal their subconscious programs patterns
          and self sabotage.
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="/services/ttc" class="grid grid-cols-12 h-24 items-center">
        <div
          class="col-span-3 bg-[url('img/about.jpg')] h-full bg-contain bg-no-repeat"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-4">THE BODY</div>
        <div class="col-span-5">TTC - SOMATIC/ENERGY WORK</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/services/iat" class="grid grid-cols-12 h-24 items-center">
        <div
          class="col-span-3 bg-[url('img/about.jpg')] h-full bg-contain bg-no-repeat"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-4">THE MIND</div>
        <div class="col-span-5">INTEGRATED ATTACHMENT THEORY</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/services/ttciat" class="grid grid-cols-12 h-24 items-center">
        <div
          class="col-span-3 bg-[url('img/about.jpg')] h-full bg-contain bg-no-repeat"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-4">THE MAGIC</div>
        <div class="col-span-5">IAT + TTC</div>
      </a>
    </div>
    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <aside class="flex flex-col items-center bg-green-400">
      <h2>Interested in working together?</h2>
      <a class="flex" href="mailto:me@example.com"> Reach out </a>
    </aside>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
